videos.description: Jordan McLaughlin nails the three from Bennie Boatwright!
videos.headline: USC's McLaughlin hits the three

videos.description: Elijah Stewart with the massive dunk, and then technical foul.
videos.headline: USC's Stewart with a big dunk

videos.description: Kobi Simmons nails the deep three from the corner!
videos.headline: Simmons hits big three for Arizona

videos.description: Kobi Simmons seems to be tripped up by a teammate, goes down and hobbles off the court in the first half. Simmons would return to the game in the second half.
videos.headline: Arizona's Simmons goes down after collision with teammate

videos.description: Allonzo Trier gets a huge dunk off an Arizona steal.
videos.headline: Trier with the dunk!

videos.description: Parker Jackson-Cartwright with the big three from the top of the key.
videos.headline: Jackson-Cartwright for three!

videos.description: Chimezie Metu makes the huge dunk but seems to fall on the landing, and limps off the floor.
videos.headline: Metu dunks big!

videos.description: Shaqquan Aaron drives hard to get the and-1 layup.
videos.headline: USC's Aaron with the and-1 layup

videos.description: Parker Jackson-Cartwright nails the deep three from the top of the key for Arizona to get the win.
videos.headline: Jackson-Cartwright with the final three!
